>
  <section id="the-fleet">
    <div class="fleet-kicker">The fleet &middot; 11 laptops</div>
    <div class="fleet-grid" role="img" aria-label="Fleet of 11 worker laptops (stsBot0..stsBot10 on the 10.0.0.0/24 LAN), 3 with per-machine incidents: stsBot3 WDAC block, stsBot7 zero-byte DLL, stsBot9 hostname resolution.">
